<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="p.euphrates;;2" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">P.Euphrates 2</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/><gap extent="7" reason="lost" unit="character"/> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Μ</unclear>αρκέ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λλ</unclear>ῳ τῷ διασημ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">οτ</unclear>άτῳ διέπο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied>ι <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τὰ</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μέ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">η τῆς</supplied> <choice><corr>ἡγεμονίας</corr><sic>ηγεμονειας</sic></choice> παρὰ Ρωσταμ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ου</supplied>

    <lb n="2"/><gap extent="6" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>υ τῶν ἀπὸ <choice><corr>Βίρθας</corr><sic>βειρθας</sic></choice> Οκβανων. <space dim="horizontal" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>

    <lb n="3"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Ταλαιπω</supplied>ρίαν πάσχων, δέσποτα, ἐπὶ σὲ  καταφεύγω καὶ ἀξιῶ εὐμενῶς προσέσθαι μου

    <lb n="4"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τὴν ἀξίω</supplied>σιν· τε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">λ</supplied>ευτῶν γὰρ, κύριε, ὁ δηλούμενός μου πατὴρ κατέλειψέν μοι ἄμπελον

    <lb n="5"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐν τῇ </supplied><choice><corr><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Β</supplied>ίρθᾳ</corr><sic><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">β</supplied>ειρθα</sic></choice> ὄντι πάνυ νεωτέρῳ· <choice><corr>συμβὰν</corr><sic>συνβα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied></sic></choice> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ὲ τὴν Περσῶν καὶ γεγενῆσθαι

    <lb n="6"/><gap extent="6" reason="lost" unit="character"/>υν μόλις ἐκφυγεῖν καὶ γενέσθαι ἐν Ἀππάδνᾳ τὴν ἐφήμερον τροφὴν πορ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>-

    <lb n="7"/><gap extent="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> μετ</supplied>ὰ δὲ ταῦτα γενομένου μου ἐν τῇ <choice><corr>Βίρθᾳ</corr><sic>βειρθα</sic></choice> καὶ βουλομένου τὴν αὐτὴν καταλει-

    <lb n="8"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">φθεῖσάν</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear>οι ἄμπελον καρπίσασθαι, Βαρσημαιας τις Θαϊμου, ἀνὴρ πάνυ βίαιος καὶ αὐθά-

    <lb n="9"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δης ὑπάρ</supplied>χων πολύ τε ἐν τοῖς τόποις δυνάμενος, οὐκ οἶδα τίνι λόγῳ ἢ ποίῳ δικαίῳ

    <lb n="10"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">χρησά</supplied>μενος διακατέσχεν τὴν αὐτὴν ἄμπελον ὡς ἀπὸ ἑξαετοῦς χρόνου μέχρις

    <lb n="11"/><supplied cert="low" reason="lost">σήμερον </supplied>, <choice><corr>καταφρονήσας</corr><sic>καταφρονενας</sic></choice> μου τῆς μετριότητος τῷ <choice><corr>μηδένα</corr><sic>μηδενα<add place="supralinear">ν</add></sic></choice> με ἔχειν μηδὲ τῶν <choice><corr>γινο-

    <lb n="12"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μένων</supplied></corr><sic>γεινο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μενων</supplied></sic></choice><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> ὑ</supplied>π᾽ ἐμοῦ ἐντυχιῶν τῷ κατὰ τόπους ἑκατοντάρχῳ φροντίδα ποιούμενος.

    <lb n="13"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐπε</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὶ</unclear> οὖν, κύρι<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε</supplied>, οὐδαμόθεν ἔχω <choice><corr>ἐκδικίας</corr><sic>εγδικιας</sic></choice> τυχεῖν ἐὰν μὴ ἡ σὴ συνεπινεύσῃ μοι τύχη,

    <lb n="14"/><choice><corr>ὀχλοῦμαι</corr><sic>οχλουμε</sic></choice> γὰρ καὶ ὑπὸ Βαθσαββαθας <choice><corr>γενομένης δανιστρίας</corr><sic>γενεμενης δανιστρη</sic></choice> τοῦ αὐτοῦ πατρός μου ᾗ καὶ <choice><corr>ὑπό-

    <lb n="15"/>κειται</corr><sic>υποκειτε</sic></choice> ἡ αὐτὴ ἄμπελος, <space dim="horizontal" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἀξιῶ καὶ δέομαα, εἴ σου τῇ τύχῃ δοκῇ, δι᾽ ὑπογραφῆς σου <choice><corr>κελεῦσαι</corr><sic>κελευσε</sic></choice>

    <lb n="16"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ῷ ἐν Ἀπ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πά</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>νᾳ ἐπιτρόπῳ <expan>Κλ<ex cert="high">αυδίῳ</ex></expan> Ἀρίστωνι, ἢ <choice><corr>ᾧ</corr><sic>ο</sic></choice> ἄν σου τῇ τύχῃ δοκῇ, τὴν τοῦ αὐτοῦ Βαρ-

    <lb n="17"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σ</unclear>ημαια <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear><gap extent="2" reason="lost" unit="character"/>, <choice><corr>κελεῦσαι</corr><sic>καιλευσε</sic></choice> δὲ αὐτῷ οὗ χρόν<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υ ἐ</supplied>καρπίσατο ἀποδοῦναί μοι τὰς προσόδους. οὕτως

    <lb n="18"/>γὰρ διὰ τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὴ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν σὴ</supplied>ν τύχην ἀνὴρ μέτριος τῶν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῶ</unclear>ν μὴ <choice><corr>στερηθεὶς</corr><sic>στερεθεις</sic></choice> καὶ <choice><corr>ἀνεπήρεαστος</corr><sic>ανεπηριαστος</sic></choice> μείνας

    <lb n="19"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἕ</supplied>ξω σοι εἰ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀεὶ εὐ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">χ</unclear>αριστεῖν. <space dim="horizontal" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>

    <lb n="20"/><handShift new="m2"/> Κλάτιος <gap extent="7" reason="lost" unit="character"/>ς <choice><corr>ἐρωτηθεὶς</corr><sic>ερωτηθις</sic></choice> ἔγραψα ὑπὲρ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">Ρωστα</supplied>μου ἀγραμμάτου <choice><corr>διαπεμψαμένου</corr><sic>διαπενψαμενου</sic></choice> τὰ <choice><corr>πιττάκια</corr><sic>πιτακια</sic></choice>.

    <lb n="21"/><handShift new="m1"/> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear><gap extent="2" reason="lost" unit="character"/>χ<gap extent="1" reason="lost" unit="character"/>ι.</ab></div><div n="meta.23922" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.23922" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="0250" notBefore="0244" type="textDate">244 - 250 (?)</date></p></div><div n="meta.23922" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Ediert in: JS 1995, S. 67 - 84. Zur Datierung vgl. S. 94.</p></div><div n="meta.23922" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Euphr.</title><biblScope type="numbers">2</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">23922</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0239</series>; <biblScope type="volume">22</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">15497</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0239;22;15497" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.23922" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">JS 1995, S. 86, Fig. 4 - 5</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.23922" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">SB XXII 15497</bibl></div><div n="meta.23922" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Birtha Okbanon</placeName> (<geogName cert="high" type="ancientRegion">Syria Coele</geogName>)</p></div><div n="meta.23922" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://byzance.dr10.cnrs.fr/web/ressources/Euphrate/P.Euphrate2r.jpg"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>